# README-Privacy-Policy
Privacy Policy for Server Saver Discord Bot


Last updated: *2024/4/21*


Server Saver ("us", "we", or "our") operates the Server Saver Discord bot . This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data.

We use your data to provide and improve the Service. By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

Information Collection and Use
We collect several different types of information for various purposes to provide and improve our Service to you.

1.Types of Data Collected


Discord User Data

We may collect your Discord user ID, username, discriminator, avatar, and other information necessary for the proper functioning of the Service.

2.Server Data


We may collect data about your Discord server, including server ID, server name, server settings, and other relevant information required for moderation purposes.

